  <!-- EN: Battle Friend -->
  <DMS_Mech_BattleFrame.label>战斗夥伴</DMS_Mech_BattleFrame.label>
  <!-- EN: Designed as a light infantry fighting unit, the battle friend has a considerable load capacity and ability to use most human equipment. -->
  <DMS_Mech_BattleFrame.description>设计为轻型步兵作战单位。战斗框架拥有相当程度的负载能力，并且能够使用大部分人类装备，\n 当它可以装备大量弹药的重型武器时，已经被部队大规模使用并部署在各种环境中也就不足为奇了。</DMS_Mech_BattleFrame.description>
  <!-- EN: head -->
  <DMS_Mech_BattleFrame.tools.head.label>头部</DMS_Mech_BattleFrame.tools.head.label>
  <!-- EN: left fist -->
  <DMS_Mech_BattleFrame.tools.left_fist.label>左拳</DMS_Mech_BattleFrame.tools.left_fist.label>
  <!-- EN: right fist -->
  <DMS_Mech_BattleFrame.tools.right_fist.label>右拳</DMS_Mech_BattleFrame.tools.right_fist.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Escort Lifter -->
  <DMS_Mech_EscortLifter.label>运输框架</DMS_Mech_EscortLifter.label>
  <!-- EN: An early stage mass-production automatroid. Its no longer in regular service but there're still plenty of them modified for transport purposes. -->
  <DMS_Mech_EscortLifter.description>战斗框架作为早期批次生产的机兵尽管已不再是标准的现役兵器但仍有很多经过改装後用於运输目的，但由於其重量与削减的火控系统因此只能装备轻武器用於自卫。</DMS_Mech_EscortLifter.description>
