  <!-- EN: Shaft Worker -->
  <DMS_Mech_ShaftWorker.label>工程驳机</DMS_Mech_ShaftWorker.label>
  <!-- EN: An early stage mass-produced automatroid. Its no longer in regular service but there're still lots of them modified to used for mining and construct purpose. -->
  <DMS_Mech_ShaftWorker.description>一种被大量用於殖民据点建设与资源开采的作业型战斗框架。具有一定的後勤能力，但由於其重量与削减的火控系统因此只能装备轻武器用於自卫</DMS_Mech_ShaftWorker.description>
